{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b19fd72d56","title":"陈伯达关于社外群众组织要求监督新华社问题的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ed9d977df2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":20,"articleId":"b19fd72d56"}],"tags":[{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"02cc8f9ddc","type":"title","text":"陈伯达关于社外群众组织要求监督新华社问题的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56"},{"id":"853f851f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"〖一月二十日，××学院五人，来新华社社长办公室，要王唯真同志签字接受其监督，被王唯真同志拒绝，并打电话报告了中央文革。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56"},{"id":"3321050ac9","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志在电话中指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56"},{"id":"10dd945827","type":"paragraph","text":"不能签字。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56"},{"id":"b080a30412","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社是党中央重点保护单位，不能冲，谁冲后果由他负责。已进驻的社外人员，请他们先退出去，以后再说。走时欢送，可开欢送会。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56"}],"page":{"id":"2ed7a7494c","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"b19fd72d56","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}